description: Consultation by the London Borough of Haringey on the approval of details for Condition 9 (Boundary treatment) of planning permission ref. HGY/2021/2727 granted on 10/10/2022 for the demolition of existing building and redevelopment of site to provide 41 new homes within 3 buildings ranging from 3 to 6 storeys in height, with associated vehicular access from Woodside Avenue, wheelchair parking, landscaping, refuse/recycling and cycle storage facilities. New stepped access to Parkland Walk from Woodside Avenue (LBH ref. HGY/2023/1120)
site_name: Cranwood100 Woodside AvenueHornseyLondonN10 3JA
